  it  was  long  awaited  that  this  socially  and educationally  backward  section  of  the  society  will  get  justice  after  this constitutional  amendment  the  national  commission  for  backward  classes  was constituted on 14th august 1993 but it did not enjoy constitutional status whereas other  commissions  enjoyed    now  this  commission  will  enjoy  constitutional status  it is being alleged that rights of the states are being taken away  this is not correct    the  states  will  continue  enjoying  their  rights  as  earlier  obcs  have  not got social justice till now  they constitute 52 per cent of the population  a socioeconomic  survey  was  conducted  in  the  year  2011  in  which  details  of  all  castes were reflected except obcs  obc constitutes of the artisans doing petty jobs  i thank the government and welcome this historical bill    